description: Yo doomers, long time no see. Iv'e been played Doom since 8th grade. And this is the cool big ass game that i ever played. I made over 20 levels for Doom 2 and i guess that i created them well. So whatever... this is one of my best wad that i ever created. It's really fun to play with your friends on coop and there's a place for deathmatching too. Hope you like it and Doom for EVVAAARR!!!
